{"tid":1391581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人地外地心繫港 外國巴絲 香港需要你！","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:36:02.000Z","uid":187578,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bb0d64ee9927720a6ff4a41d939c3960e2b6093c","tid":1391581,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"【對鬼仔學生專用文宣】 (Scroll down for English)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召喚海外留學生，幫手喺大學度周圍貼文宣海報<br />\n咁多位隨便cop啲走幫幫手share唔該唔該<br />\n</span></span><br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n致  海外留學嘅香港學生，<span style=\"color: red;\">請幫拖將香港嘅事揚出國際：<br />\n</span><br />\n呢個係遍地開花作戰計劃，喺大學嘅校園内，周圍貼宣傳海報，撕一貼百，唔好局限喺一塊連儂牆上。不現身不露面，流水式宣傳，違反校規唔緊要，最緊要唔好比人捉倒。<br />\n<br />\n以下提供對鬼仔大學生專用嘅文宣海報，適合A3，請自行印刷，呼籲咁多位都幫手整幾張。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港宜家最需要嘅係國際救援同外國政府施壓，將議題打入大學校園，引起討論同關注。最好貼去政治社會學department，佢地最有興趣。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n行動比蝗學生阻攔騷擾嘅話，記得影住佢地然後call實Q，等佢地柒出太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想同蝗學生正面衝突嘅，盡量入夜人少先貼，切勿單獨行動。<br />\n<br />\n海報下可自行加句&ldquo;This poster is produced by the Hong Kong students at xxx University.&rdquo;嚟防止比校方話係來歷不明嘅海報而銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n[Liberate HK Posters dedicated to western universities]<br />\n<br />\nDear international Hong Kong university students, <br />\n<br />\nPlease stick these posters around the university campus to spread the news of Hong Kong. Don&rsquo;t just stick them on Lennon Walls &ndash; stick them anywhere you like. It&rsquo;s okay to break the school rules, as long as you don&rsquo;t get caught. <br />\n<br />\nThese posters can be printed in A3 size, print them yourselves please. And feel free to create more posters. <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong has to raise the awareness of the international community in order to be saved, so we&rsquo;re taking it to the academic community. Stick the posters to the departments of politics and social sciences, bet they&rsquo;d love to discuss about it. <br />\n<br />\nFor safety concerns, if the mainland students came to interfere, call the university security immediately, and remember to film them. <br />\n<br />\nIf you want to avoid conflicts with other students, do it at midnight when nobody is watching. <br />\n<br />\nYou might want to add a line at the bottom of the poster saying: &ldquo;This poster is produced by the Hong Kong students at xxx University.&rdquo; to prevent it from being removed by university staff. <br />\n<br />\nGood Luck everybody. LONG LIVE HONG KONG.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ShmxqL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ShmxqL.png&h=1fb163f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCsxD5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCsxD5M.png&h=46663db4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OsP4vcs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOsP4vcs.png&h=209e53d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVuj3xt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVuj3xt.png&h=aa613232&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K3ugmi9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK3ugmi9.png&h=174c740d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ojoLLP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ojoLLP.png&h=bafbbec3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajnYzEa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajnYzEa.png&h=a6e2c16a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiNaqLR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiNaqLR.png&h=b1af7640&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3gizEc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3gizEc.png&h=898f3ef5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b487430f3d4e4d29ccf41ba0ce112817c26c0fe","tid":1391581,"uid":220864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"[突發] 獨立調查委員會報告出咗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtJuuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtJuuS</a>"},{"pid":"d1db7e31fb4468c92870a865c084ed9f36e60552","tid":1391581,"uid":187578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"原po: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100020285587575/posts/368430757176441?s=100005841185148&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100020285587575%2Fposts%2F368430757176441%3Fs%3D100005841185148%26sfns%3Dmo&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=6c6bc455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100020285587575/posts/368430757176441?s=100005841185148&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8959f8a2435a32cbda901530cb547ef4257d8bfa","tid":1391581,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"94b3a1babeb743e72cfde134d082bd37859255c4","tid":1391581,"uid":187755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:12:50.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"73e19a9fa6d11d6e72ae2a4a4e5fa7d52de63b6e","tid":1391581,"uid":187578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"鍾庭耀博士開始抽樣找人做民調 panel ，一個係抽樣調查panel ， 一個係自願panel ， register 自願panel 就會定期收到民調問卷，譬如港鐵不合作運動的看法，港澳辦的記者會個人看法等，包括林鄭rating 等等。請大家務必參與，讓民意走向有普遍認受性。<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel?fbclid=IwAR1177tmo1mLixsGdqAPklovoNlZFy9Kn8vB1p5F0uvvmgOB3W-6KuZjIk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1177tmo1mLixsGdqAPklovoNlZFy9Kn8vB1p5F0uvvmgOB3W-6KuZjIk4&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFnwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=b9a3c543\" da